	dprr:hasNoteText "Aed. cur., uncertain date. He put on a revival performance of the Andria of Terence (J. Heurgon, REL 27, 1949, 106-108). See the text and apparatus of Donatus, Commentum Terenti (ed. Wessner) 1, p. 36, on the Didascalia to the Andria, Praefatio 6.\n" .
